snippet.title: The Catch: Carp & Coarse | Announce trailer | PS4
snippet.description: It’s time to fish somewhere new. Let’s go on the hunt for the catch of a lifetime in The Catch: Carp & Coarse. Coming to PlayStation 4 this summer. Legendary boss fish across 35 species - let’s go land a monster!
